column5: Another few days spent in paradise. If you want to avoid the canoeing and the scenery, go directly to 3:30 for a not-bad smallmouth:  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dzBKVQ7cEkc
Killarney is a beautiful area for sure, thanks for the video.
Never been to Killarney  .  Now I want to go so badly. Thanks for the awesome video!
Really nice fish but I liked the intro better!
Truely enjoyed Dave.  Great job on the vid. Fingers and all.
